✅ Privacy Policy for LearnQuest AI
Effective Date: April 17, 2025

At LearnQuest AI, developed by SmartDevs, we respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information.

🔒 Information We Collect
Email address (only when you sign in via Google or email)

Usage data (such as feature interactions for improving the app)

Device information (like device model and OS version for crash reports)

🛡️ How We Use Your Information
To provide and maintain our services

To personalize your learning experience

To communicate with you regarding updates or support

To improve app performance and fix bugs

🤝 Third-Party Services
We use Firebase (by Google) for authentication and database services. Google may collect some basic information for login and analytics purposes.

❌ What We Don’t Do
We do not sell your personal data.

We do not track you outside of LearnQuest AI.

📞 Contact Us
If you have any questions about this policy, email us at support@smartdevs.com.
